title: Washington Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This deli and caterer has a separate vegan menu that includes vegan pizza (using Teese) available daily by the slice, a vegan meatball sub, tofurkey reuben, tofu sandwich, coleslaw, potato salad. Can make vegan sheet cakes for catering orders.
